Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自己的生命為代價…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
