Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是和葉姐姐對吧
